Package com.intellij.openapi.externalSystem.service.remote

Interface RemoteExternalSystemProgressNotificationManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExternalSystemProgressNotificationManagerImpl

    public interface RemoteExternalSystemProgressNotificationManager
extends java.rmi.Remote
    Defines interface for the entity that manages notifications about progress of long-running operations performed at external system API side.

    Implementations of this interface are expected to be thread-safe.
